"6:27:11" : {s: 6, a: 27, w: 11, r: "كذب", t: "نُكَذِّبَ", l: "كَذَّبَ", lc: 176, tl: "nukadhiba", lb: "অস্বীকার করা",e: "we would deny", b: "অস্বীকার করতাম (না)", i: "kami akan mendustakan", f: 1, rm: "To lie, say what is not a fact, lie to falsely invent, tell lies about or against, fabricate a lie, relate a lie, say a falsehood, be wrong, be cut off, deceive, disappoint the expectation of."},
